        &lt;a href="https://virtuoso-performance.com/comment/21#comment-21" class="permalink" rel="bookmark" hreflang="en"&gt;sad -- a structural isse&lt;/a&gt;        &lt;mark class="comment__new marker marker--success hidden" data-comment-timestamp="1490646171"&gt;&lt;/mark&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
      &lt;div class="comment__meta"&gt;
      
      &lt;div class="comment__submitted"&gt;
        &lt;span class="comment__author"&gt;&lt;span rel="schema:author"&gt;&lt;span lang="" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;John_B (not verified)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
